description:
Nelson Mandela - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/media/e/14011/t/nelson-mandela

In 2016, Pastor Doug and the Amazing Facts team traveled to South Africa to share the gospel, conduct training, and sow seeds of revival and reformation in its three largest citiesCape Town, Durban, and Johannesburg. God did amazing things in this beautiful land known for diamonds and big game parks.
